	● There's a book suitable for each level
	● Fully integrates the teaching of grammar and oral communication skills
● Integrated skills focus:
	1. Features a large array of written and oral exercises, including oral drills, dialog writing, and sentence writing

	2. Contains clear, concise, "User-friendly" grammar charts with examples and explanations in simple English

	3. Exercises are thorough, well-written and immensely useful in leading to a working knowledge of everyday American English

	● Can be used as a course text, reference book, or supplementary material
	● Options in either full or split editions of the student book, workbook, and teacher's guide
	● Available with Chinese-English Edition





